data.description: Absolutely stunning home with so many extra features and space that you will not want to miss only two minutes from the square. This 3 bedroom, 3.5 bathroom home has a beautifully renovated kitchen and owner’s suite bathroom with new cabinets, lighting, countertops, flooring, paint, & so much more! As you walk into this gorgeous home you will experience the beautiful wood floors which lead to a formal living room along with a stunning fireplace with crown molding throughout the home. What home has a formal living room, a family room, a den, and full size dining room that provide so much extra space for you and your family. This home also has a HUGE basement with a kitchen, separate living space, and a half bath that offers ELEVATOR access. The garage also offers endless storage space.
